data.description: Welcome home to this beautifully renovated 5 bed, 3 bath sprawling ranch located on a spacious 3 acre lot! The minute you pull up, you'll be charmed by the convenient circle drive and oversized porte cochere that can fit multiple vehicles. The inside won't disappoint either! The minute you walk through the front door, you’ll see that this home has been recently updated with new flooring, fresh paint and luxury touches around every corner. The great room is absolutely massive and boasts oversized windows that allow for a flood of natural light. With almost 1,000 square foot in just the great room alone, there is plenty of room for entertaining or a large family. The open concept kitchen has been tastefully updated and overlooks the great room. The kitchen features plenty of counter space, ample storage with tons of cabinets, walk-in pantry, brand new tile backsplash, stylish brick floors, and a full suite of stainless steel appliances that come with! This home offers plenty of seating between the kitchen's massive peninsula and the open concept dining area. Down the hall you’ll find the spacious master suite with walk-in closet and en-suite bathroom. The spa-like master bathroom features a brand new custom dual vanity with quartz countertops and tons of storage. No expense was spared on the walk-in shower that features stylish tile, shower bench, oversized niche, and a total of eight shower heads! Don’t miss the freestanding soaker tub, bidet, integrated bluetooth speaker, and the adjustable mirror - making it easy to get ready! On this wing of the home, you’ll also find two more bedrooms, a convenient laundry room, the home office and a fully updated bathroom. Right off the great room is the family room that leads to two more bedrooms and another full bathroom. The basement is perfect for a home theater with a built-in speaker system, projector screen, and hidden wiring for a projector. In the utility room you’ll notice this home has an instant water heater, updated electric, updated plumbing and a ton of storage. The backyard is an entertainer’s dream, with the oversized two tiered deck, a separate large patio, the fire pit and the above-ground pool with a custom deck. The yard also features a large fenced-in garden, chicken coop, garden shed, and detached two car garage with entrances on both sides! The main house also includes attached garage space for up to four cars for a total storage space of six cars! Homes like this don't come along often, so schedule your showing today!
